    "title": "Mid-Level Frontend Developer at Schneider Electric India",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Schneider Electric India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Frontend Developer to strengthen our Mumbai-based team.\n\nAbout Schneider Electric India:\nSchneider Electric India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Schneider Electric India!",
